Combine first 6 ingredients in a large zip-top plastic bag. Add steak; seal bag, and marinate in refrigerator 8 hours or overnight. Prepare grill. Remove steak from bag, discarding marinade. Place on grill rack, and grill 8 minutes on each side or until desired degree of doneness. Let steak stand 5 minutes. Cut steak diagonally across grain into thin slices. Serve steak with Avocado-Mango Salsa.